name: BluetoothRemoteGATTDescriptor.uuid
description: The BluetoothRemoteGATTDescriptor.uuid read-only property returns the UUID of the characteristic descriptor, for example '00002902-0000-1000-8000-00805f9b34fb' for theClient Characteristic Configuration descriptor.
